title: IAA Tonight | Our 2022 NFL Bold Predictions AND Tampa Bay Buccaneers Season Preview
description: NFL regular season is set to kickoff tomorrow and LeSean McCoy, Adam Pacman Jones and Leger Douzable are here to provide you with their bold predictions for the 2022 season. Find out who Shady believes will win league MVP, who Pac thinks will win Defensive Player of the Year, and who Douz believes will win Rookie of the Year. Plus, we end the Countdown to Kickoff with the Tampa Bay Buccaneers. Will Brady and the crew bounceback from a tough playoff loss the Super Bowl Champion LA Rams?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (LeSean McCoy, Adam Pacman Jones, Leger Douzable)
